- AmenityPicker component (see skills/admin-module.md)

### AmenityPicker Component
File: apps/admin/components/AmenityPicker.tsx

Behaviour:
1. Fetch GET /api/amenities on mount
2. Display popular amenities (is_popular = true) as icon checkbox grid
   - Each item: Lucide icon + name + checkbox
   - Grouped by category
3. Below grid: custom amenity input
   - Text field for name
   - Icon selector dropdown (searchable list of Lucide icon names)
   - "Add" button → POST to /api/amenities (creates with is_popular = false)
4. Selected amenities shown as icon pills below picker
5. On room type save → write selected amenity IDs to RoomTypeAmenity

---

## API ROUTES NEEDED
- GET /api/amenities → all amenities, popular first
- POST /api/amenities → create custom amenity { name, icon, category }
- GET /api/admin/bookings?page=&status=&search= → paginated
- GET /api/admin/bookings/[id] → single booking
- PATCH /api/admin/bookings/[id] → update status
- GET /api/admin/properties/[id]/rooms → list room types
- POST /api/admin/properties/[id]/rooms → create room type + amenities
- PATCH /api/admin/properties/[id]/rooms/[roomId] → update room type + amenities
- DELETE /api/admin/properties/[id]/rooms/[roomId] → delete room type

